        "text_JTHhc6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Cedar Hospitality endeavors to ensure that all of our customers are satisfied with their purchases. To help us deliver on our customer satisfaction goals and set realistic expectations, we have provided the below-detailed information with regards to our delivery processes and procedures. These terms and conditions apply to all purchases made from Cedar Hospitality Pty Ltd (herein referred to as “Cedar”)</p><p>Confirmed orders placed online before 3pm AEST on Monday to Friday will be picked, packed and dispatched from our Melbourne warehouse within 1 - 5 days. <br/><br/>For any delays or issues regarding your order, check your account online or we will notify you via phone or email.<br/><br/></p>",
